1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 54 =

20
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:43,340
What would you like to eat for breakfast?

21
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:47,060
If you want to have a change of diet,

22
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:51,100
I can ask Liaozi to go out early in the morning

23
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:55,580
to buy desserts you like.

24
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:01,140
Your Majesty,

25
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:09,940
let my uncle be Commissioner of Palace Attendants.

26
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:15,860
You’ve agreed

27
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:17,420
to give him the post?

28
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,580
I heard from aunt

29
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:29,540
those officials just wouldn’t

30
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:32,220
let go of him being Supervisor of Finance,

31
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:34,660
saying my uncle

32
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:37,220
was only promoted

33
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:38,140
because of Your Majesty’s favor to me.

34
00:02:39,220 --> 00:02:40,420
Supervisor of Finance

35
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,020
is a significantly important post.

36
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:43,740
Uncle and I

37
00:02:44,460 --> 00:02:46,300
could use that to wreck the state.

38
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:00,380
Your Majesty,

39
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:11,660
give him that Commissioner post,

40
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,260
please?

41
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:15,780
Let them win.

42
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:17,420
He won’t be Supervisor of Finance.

43
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:26,820
Your Majesty.

44
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:29,940
Go to sleep.

45
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,860
It just came to me that I need

46
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:33,100
to fulfill some unfinished business.

47
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,180
Your Majesty,

48
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:40,140
just appoint him Commissioner,

49
00:03:40,540 --> 00:03:41,340
please?

50
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:44,860
You wanted

51
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:46,620
to see me today

52
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:48,380
for that post, didn’t you?

53
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:51,460
Those officials didn’t support my uncle

54
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:52,780
to be Supervisor of Finance

55
00:03:53,740 --> 00:03:55,540
in case I’d interfere in state affairs through him.

56
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:57,860
That’s fine.

57
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,340
But as the Noble Consort’s uncle,

58
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:02,700
he should have a decent title, right?

59
00:04:04,820 --> 00:04:07,300
Let him be Commissioner, please?

60
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:17,860
Fine.

61
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:44,980
Here you are, sir.

62
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:46,300
Please enjoy.

63
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:48,300
Three coppers.

64
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:02,940
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =
Greetings.

65
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:05,820
Sir...

66
00:05:06,540 --> 00:05:08,260
I’m here on behalf of my two old friends

67
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:09,980
Fu Bi and Han Qi

68
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:12,540
= Yelv Hongji =
to invite you and a few others

69
00:05:12,980 --> 00:05:15,100
to Mr. Zhao’s garden.

70
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:18,180
There we can enjoy the view, go fishing,

71
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:18,980
drink together and listen to music.

72
00:05:22,460 --> 00:05:23,780
Mr. Han and Mr. Fu

73
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:24,780
came to the Capital with the delegation

74
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:26,060
to celebrate Qianuan Festival.

75
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,900
My rank is too low

76
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,100
to pay respects

77
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,260
to His Majesty in person,

78
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:32,420
yet Mr. Fu and Mr. Han

79
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:33,700
entrusted you to invite me

80
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,500
for our friendship built during the trip.

81
00:05:35,820 --> 00:05:36,820
I’m greatly honored.

82
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:39,060
You can call me Acha.

83
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:42,740
Mr. Acha, please.

84
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:43,740
Please.

85
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:52,620
Please.

86
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:17,060
Father,

87
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,660
does that Khitan prince

88
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:21,780
also understand our literature?

89
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:25,220
Han Qi said he’s not bad.

90
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:29,060
At least, he’s better than you.

91
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:31,900
Oh, no!

92
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,740
Aren’t we going to lose?

93
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:35,980
There won’t be a match.

94
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:39,820
Other than competing against Khitan,

95
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,220
what else can we do?

96
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:43,620
Must we

97
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:45,060
be competitors?

98
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:51,020
Our neighbor can also be our friend

99
00:06:51,340 --> 00:06:52,180
or brother.

100
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:02,580
To play this drinking game,

101
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,460
roll the dice first,

102
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:09,780
and then the attendant

103
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:13,100
will pass the jade barrel

104
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:16,500
to the chosen person

105
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:17,780
and let him draw a stick.

106
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:23,020
The stick can decide

107
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:28,820
who will drink and how much he’ll drink.

108
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:30,740
There are rewards and punishments, too.

109
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:32,660
Sounds interesting.

110
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:34,460
You even have

111
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:35,940
so many fun games for drinking.

112
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:49,220
Greetings. Noble Consort.

113
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:54,740
Is His Majesty back from the Hall of Celebration?

114
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:56,780
His Majesty came back

115
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,460
two hours ago,

116
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,660
and then went out

117
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:03,260
with the princess and the Empress.

118
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:06,340
What?

119
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:09,660
After the celebration,

120
00:08:10,020 --> 00:08:10,940
His Majesty went out

121
00:08:10,940 --> 00:08:12,420
with the Empress and the princess

122
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:15,180
to meet with a guest.

123
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:29,820
Good day, Noble Consort.

124
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,660
This is strange.

125
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:39,500
Other than drawing “Guest drinks a full cup”

126
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:41,420
and “The attendant drinks half a cup” once each,

127
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,580
how come it was always the host that had to drink?

128
00:08:44,740 --> 00:08:46,420
Either “The host drinks half a cup”

129
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:48,260
or “The host drinks a full cup”.

130
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:06,620
= Cui Bai, courtesy name Zixi =

131
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,580
“Don’t do unto others
what you don’t want others to do unto you”.

132
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:20,740
Pass.

133
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:23,740
Mr. Ouyang didn’t

134
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:24,900
draw that stick.

135
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,740
How could it not be?

136
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:28,500
It was that one.

137
00:09:39,180 --> 00:09:40,340
It was this one.

138
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,620
There’s a dent on the tip of it.

139
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:44,180
I remember it because I had it earlier.

140
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:51,420
Read it.

141
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,300
“After hearing music in the State of Qi,

142
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,580
Confucius couldn’t smell meat for three months”.

143
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,100
The host should drink half a cup.

144
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:10,580
Thank you, Ouyang and Cui Bai.

145
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:13,940
I’m rewarded with more liquor.

146
00:10:14,100 --> 00:10:15,060
Today is a good day.

147
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:15,780
I can drink more.

148
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,300
Wonderful, Mr. Zhao!

149
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:19,220
I’ll drink a cup with you.

150
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,420
But Mr. Ouyang

151
00:10:26,420 --> 00:10:27,980
and Mr. Cui cheated.

152
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,060
Shouldn’t they be punished?

153
00:10:32,140 --> 00:10:34,180
Punish them to do something fun.

154
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:37,460
I’m lucky to meet with Mr. Ouyang

155
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:38,780
and Mr. Cui today.

156
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,340
I admire them a lot

157
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:41,940
and hope to see more of their talents.

158
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:44,180
So I propose that Mr. Ouyang and Mr. Cui

159
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,140
perform for us.

160
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,540
The form isn’t limited.

161
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:49,660
I apologize if my proposal is abrupt.

162
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:54,820
That’s a good idea.

163
00:10:55,100 --> 00:10:56,740
I haven’t seen Zixi and Yongshu’s performances

164
00:10:56,940 --> 00:10:58,860
for a long time.

165
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:01,300
Fine.

166
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:03,540
I’ll go first.

167
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,700
I knew

168
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:15,100
we’d play drinking games today,

169
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:16,700
so I brought this with me

170
00:11:17,340 --> 00:11:18,820
to entertain you.

171
00:11:54,420 --> 00:12:00,660
♪ Chu River runs for thousands of miles ♪

172
00:12:01,540 --> 00:12:10,260
♪ Alone in the Moon Tower, depressed ♪

173
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:20,540
♪ Autumn is coming ♪

174
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:29,020
♪ Looking over the 12 peaks of Wushan Mountain ♪

175
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:30,340
= Yan Jidao =

176
00:12:30,340 --> 00:12:38,100
♪ Fair skin as beautiful as flowers ♪

177
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:45,580
♪ Fairies are in the high tower ♪

178
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:57,220
An amazing play with a beautiful tune.

179
00:12:58,060 --> 00:13:00,740
Tragedies are always more memorable,

180
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:02,380
but

181
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:04,900
as an ordinary man,

182
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:09,900
I prefer happy endings.

183
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:11,940
Not all couples

184
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:13,740
should end up apart and depressed.

185
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:16,020
A great chance is right in front of you.

186
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,420
Why don’t you grab it?

187
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:26,060
Is Mr. Cui in love with someone

188
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:27,620
but can’t be with her?

189
00:13:28,660 --> 00:13:30,540
Mr. Zhao may be able to help.

190
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:32,540
Mr. Cui,

191
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:34,580
don’t you always adore

192
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:36,380
Mrs. Zhao’s maid?

193
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:38,940
Why don’t you take this chance to propose to her?

194
00:13:39,340 --> 00:13:41,300
I can be your matchmaker.

195
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:42,780
Me, too.

196
00:13:44,740 --> 00:13:47,340
My wife regards her

197
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:49,220
as her little sister.

198
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,940
If you want her to be your concubine...

199
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:57,060
I dare not.

200
00:13:58,660 --> 00:14:00,260
If I have the honor

201
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:01,980
to be with your maid

202
00:14:01,980 --> 00:14:02,940
Miss Qiuhe,

203
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:05,740
she’ll be my one and only wife.

204
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:08,700
I’ll have no more desires.

205
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:14,020
I need to ask my wife

206
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:14,940
and my daughter first.

207
00:14:15,820 --> 00:14:17,940
They’re over there behind the curtain.

208
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:20,180
Wait a minute.

209
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:31,980
Give me the puppet.

210
00:14:46,820 --> 00:14:48,060
Miss Zhao said

211
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:50,820
if you can give her a gift,

212
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:52,860
she’ll speak to Mrs. Zhao

213
00:14:53,060 --> 00:14:54,100
for you.

214
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:55,820
What does she want?

215
00:14:57,140 --> 00:14:59,580
She wants

216
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:01,300
the puppet you made

217
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:03,100
because she’s never seen

218
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:04,260
such a lifelike doll before.

219
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:06,740
That’s all?

220
00:15:14,060 --> 00:15:15,460
She can have it.

221
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:18,020
When I prepare the betrothal presents,

222
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:20,980
I’ll make better ones for her.

223
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:24,220
I don’t know

224
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:26,140
how to repay Mrs. Zhao’s and Miss Zhao’s kindness.

225
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:31,020
If Qiuhe can marry a good husband,

226
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:32,740
my wife and daughter

227
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,540
must be happy for her.

228
00:15:35,380 --> 00:15:36,780
If you mistreat her,

229
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:38,260
I won’t turn a blind eye to it.

230
00:15:38,820 --> 00:15:39,460
Yes.

231
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:42,740
Your Highness,

232
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:45,740
you don’t want Qiuhe to leave?

233
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,940
I’m happy for her.

234
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:55,060
Women’s greatest luck

235
00:15:56,500 --> 00:15:58,620
is to be able to marry

236
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:00,940
people they love.

237
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:08,620
Father can marry Qiuhe to her love

238
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:11,580
but insists on marrying me to Li Wei.

239
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:17,940
Huirou,

240
00:16:18,036 --> 00:16:18,843
you...

241
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:20,900
Your Highness,

242
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:24,260
I am happy for Qiuhe.

243
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:28,420
I don’t blame father.

244
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:31,580
He cares about Qiuhe’s

245
00:16:32,180 --> 00:16:34,060
and Cui Bai’s feelings,

246
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:36,700
I’m sure...

247
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:39,620
I’m sure he wouldn’t ignore mine.

248
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,660
I guess

249
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:46,020
he has other concerns.

250
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:56,940
Noble Consort, His Majesty isn’t back yet.

251
00:16:57,740 --> 00:16:59,060
Today is his birthday.

252
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:01,020
I’ll wait for him.

253
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:20,580
♪ Lotuses bloom outside the cool water palace ♪

254
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:27,540
♪ Holm oaks bathe in the sun ♪

255
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:34,340
♪ Emperor’s carriage arrives as the tune sounds ♪

256
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:40,660
♪ Reports bearing good news are all over the bed ♪

257
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:50,460
♪ Incense is burned in the jade censer ♪

258
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:56,860
♪ Emperor’s kindness grows with time ♪

259
00:17:57,260 --> 00:18:04,300
♪ News came again that prisons are empty ♪

260
00:18:04,940 --> 00:18:09,780
♪ Maids are holding cups for toasts ♪

261
00:18:10,220 --> 00:18:16,220
♪ Incense is burned in the jade censer ♪

262
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:23,020
♪ Emperor’s kindness grows with time ♪

263
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:30,260
♪ News came again that prisons are empty ♪

264
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:36,420
♪ Maids are holding cups for toasts ♪

265
00:18:37,540 --> 00:18:46,500
♪ Maids are holding cups for toasts ♪

266
00:19:02,340 --> 00:19:05,100
Jidao’s new verse is elegant

267
00:19:05,100 --> 00:19:06,020
and graceful.

268
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:07,660
It’s perfect for the occasion.

269
00:19:08,460 --> 00:19:10,420
It celebrates the Emperor of Song’s birthday,

270
00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:13,380
which fits the time seamlessly.

271
00:19:15,140 --> 00:19:16,300
On my way here,

272
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:18,820
I witnessed your country’s prosperity

273
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:19,940
and the well-off life your people are living.

274
00:19:20,580 --> 00:19:21,940
Not to mention the countless talents you have.

275
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:23,140
All are thriving.

276
00:19:24,260 --> 00:19:26,420
I wish I were born here.

277
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:28,940
But

278
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:33,620
why did he sing that verse?

279
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:37,860
It’s Acha’s turn to roll the dice.

280
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:02,540
This one is spot-on.

281
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:11,580
“Isn’t it a delight to have friends
coming from afar?”

282
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:13,620
The guest should drink half a cup.

283
00:20:16,020 --> 00:20:16,740
Let’s drink.

284
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:34,740
To be honest,

285
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,380
I think I know

286
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:38,260
who you really are, Mr. Zhao.

287
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,340
I know your real name, too.

288
00:20:42,740 --> 00:20:43,980
I shouldn’t have left home

289
00:20:44,220 --> 00:20:45,260
and come all the way here

290
00:20:46,300 --> 00:20:47,660
without telling my parents.

291
00:20:48,460 --> 00:20:49,740
Were our relationship destroyed because of me,

292
00:20:49,740 --> 00:20:50,620
my death wouldn’t be enough to pay for the damage.

293
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,380
Yet you didn’t blame me

294
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:55,740
but treat me generously as a friend.

295
00:20:57,220 --> 00:20:58,700
I’m ashamed of myself

296
00:21:00,180 --> 00:21:01,380
but admire you greatly.

297
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:05,140
Your friends and subordinates

298
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:07,260
also impress me.

299
00:21:08,460 --> 00:21:10,140
Jidao is younger

300
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:12,060
but much more talented than me.

301
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:13,980
I can’t imagine

302
00:21:13,980 --> 00:21:15,260
how great Mr. Zhao is.

303
00:21:18,140 --> 00:21:20,260
In terms of literature and art,

304
00:21:20,300 --> 00:21:21,660
I’m not even

305
00:21:21,660 --> 00:21:23,780
as good as their students.

306
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:27,300
My talent isn’t worth mentioning.

307
00:21:33,780 --> 00:21:35,500
Come with me.

308
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:13,820
I like poetry, books and paintings

309
00:22:14,780 --> 00:22:16,780
and love those who create them.

310
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:18,820
But

311
00:22:18,820 --> 00:22:20,340
I’ve never spent too much time

312
00:22:20,540 --> 00:22:21,580
honing my skills.

313
00:22:22,820 --> 00:22:23,740
Why?

314
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:26,580
Song is well-known

315
00:22:26,580 --> 00:22:28,100
for literature and art.

316
00:22:28,940 --> 00:22:29,780
Acha,

317
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:31,860
throughout our lives,

318
00:22:32,340 --> 00:22:34,900
we no longer have the chance to paint,

319
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:36,620
but

320
00:22:38,300 --> 00:22:40,180
the world still needs

321
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:42,180
to be colored carefully.

322
00:22:43,740 --> 00:22:45,500
I appreciate that you said our state

323
00:22:46,260 --> 00:22:48,500
is prosperous with countless talents.

324
00:22:49,660 --> 00:22:51,780
I hope whenever our next meeting is,

325
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:56,260
they can still write and paint,

326
00:22:56,380 --> 00:22:57,460
and play the instrument freely.

327
00:22:57,740 --> 00:22:58,620
And they can still

328
00:22:58,940 --> 00:23:01,580
drink and play games with friends from afar

329
00:23:02,540 --> 00:23:03,820
so that our effort today won’t be in vain.

330
00:23:19,780 --> 00:23:20,980
Today is Your Majesty’s birthday.

331
00:23:21,660 --> 00:23:23,660
My uncle, aunt, cousin

332
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:25,180
and I

333
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:27,180
prepared these presents for you.

334
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:30,180
Do you like them?

335
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:32,940
Bihan,

336
00:23:34,260 --> 00:23:35,260
you know

337
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:39,220
I don’t care much

338
00:23:39,540 --> 00:23:40,700
about valuables like these.

339
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:42,540
On my birthday,

340
00:23:43,540 --> 00:23:45,340
other than the routine celebration,

341
00:23:46,980 --> 00:23:48,420
if I can have

342
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:50,100
a bowl of mutton noodles you made,

343
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,460
that will be great.

344
00:23:57,020 --> 00:23:58,100
So you’re

345
00:23:58,700 --> 00:24:00,140
waiting for my noodles.

346
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:02,060
I’ll

347
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:04,700
make some for you now.

348
00:24:11,460 --> 00:24:12,300
Today...

349
00:24:14,580 --> 00:24:16,460
Today, I went out with the Empress

350
00:24:17,140 --> 00:24:18,500
for business.

351
00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:20,860
I couldn’t tell you in advance.

352
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:22,220
Business?

353
00:24:24,020 --> 00:24:25,820
I didn’t realize until today

354
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:28,700
that your private and state businesses

355
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:32,260
are inseparable.

356
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:44,660
You said you don’t care

357
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:48,420
about these things

358
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:50,780
but you dumped them

359
00:24:51,300 --> 00:24:52,220
on me.

360
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:57,140
Bihan,

361
00:24:58,100 --> 00:24:59,380
you know I...

362
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:25,100
You know

363
00:25:27,100 --> 00:25:28,460
I gave you those

364
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:30,460
to make you happy.

365
00:25:30,460 --> 00:25:31,340
How could you say

366
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,220
I dumped on you

367
00:25:34,220 --> 00:25:36,340
what I didn’t care?

368
00:25:38,580 --> 00:25:39,420
Now,

369
00:25:40,820 --> 00:25:42,700
you can give me something you do care.

370
00:25:52,620 --> 00:25:53,300
Fine.

371
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:56,140
Don’t you want your uncle

372
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:57,220
to be Commissioner of Palace Attendants?

373
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,020
He can have that.

374
00:26:01,020 --> 00:26:02,260
I’ll also issue a decree

375
00:26:03,300 --> 00:26:05,020
to promote him to Governor of Huaikang

376
00:26:05,020 --> 00:26:06,020
and Chief of the Palace of Sage

377
00:26:10,100 --> 00:26:11,620
but I’ll also make it clear

378
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:15,300
that from now on, family members of the harem

379
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:18,100
cannot be in the Cabinet or Privy Council.

380
00:26:24,740 --> 00:26:25,540
Alright.

381
00:26:27,620 --> 00:26:29,180
I’ll keep my promise.

382
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:31,940
I’m tired

383
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:33,340
and going to rest.

384
00:26:36,540 --> 00:26:37,820
Go back

385
00:26:37,900 --> 00:26:39,340
with the gifts

386
00:26:39,820 --> 00:26:40,900
your uncle prepared.

387
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:59,460
= Boundary of Xiuzhou =

388
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:39,780
Court adjourned.

389
00:27:55,100 --> 00:27:56,820
= Bao Zheng, courtesy name Xiren =

390
00:27:56,820 --> 00:27:58,340
Xiuzhou’s earthquake earlier

391
00:27:58,940 --> 00:28:00,500
is a warning from heaven

392
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:03,300
that the court is polluted

393
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:05,700
and the evildoer is hiding in the shadow.

394
00:28:06,460 --> 00:28:08,500
That is the shameless Zhang Yaozuo

395
00:28:08,660 --> 00:28:10,620
who’s made no contribution whatsoever

396
00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:13,500
but holding a high-ranking post.

397
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:16,500
= Wang Juzheng, courtesy name Bozhong =
Empress Dowager Zhaoxian

398
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:17,780
gave birth to the Founding Father and his brother

399
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:20,100
whose younger brother

400
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:22,660
only ended up as a governor.

401
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:24,940
Former Vice Minister of Works Lei Youzhong

402
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,620
was only appointed
Commissioner of Palace Attendants

403
00:28:26,660 --> 00:28:27,940
after appeasing Xichuan.

404
00:28:28,380 --> 00:28:31,140
Zheng Jian was Chief Executive of Privy Council

405
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:33,780
and governed Bingzhou as Scholar of Politics

406
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,500
before becoming Commissioner of Palace Attendants.

407
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:38,340
Neither is Zhang Yaozuo closer to

408
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,940
the royal family than
Empress Dowager Zhaoxian’s brother

409
00:28:41,620 --> 00:28:42,500
nor is he

410
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:44,980
more capable than Lei Youzhong and Zheng Jian.

411
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:49,060
Yet he’s Commissioner of Palace Attendants,

412
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:50,660
Chief of the Palace of Sage and
Governor of Huaikang.

413
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:59,060
Everyone,

414
00:28:59,060 --> 00:29:01,060
please don’t leave yet.

415
00:29:02,540 --> 00:29:05,260
I’m going to remonstrate with His Majesty

416
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:08,020
together with all the censors

417
00:29:08,900 --> 00:29:11,860
about promoting Zhang Yaozuo to Commissioner

418
00:29:12,100 --> 00:29:13,980
and Governor of Huaikang.

419
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:16,220
Remonstrance Bureau will join the Censorate.

420
00:29:31,940 --> 00:29:33,900
This sachet is exquisitely made.

421
00:29:34,460 --> 00:29:36,300
I sewed it especially for you.

422
00:29:36,700 --> 00:29:37,740
Thank you so much.

423
00:29:39,973 --> 00:29:40,663
Look.

424
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:42,370
How skilled she is!

425
00:29:42,463 --> 00:29:44,180
Too bad the spice inside

426
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:45,380
isn’t of the highest quality.

427
00:29:46,380 --> 00:29:48,140
Qiuhe is married.

428
00:29:48,860 --> 00:29:51,780
Although she visits Her Highness regularly,

429
00:29:52,420 --> 00:29:53,700
we can’t always

430
00:29:53,940 --> 00:29:55,420
ask her to make things for us.

431
00:29:56,020 --> 00:29:57,380
Madam, princess!

432
00:29:58,540 --> 00:29:59,260
Princess!

433
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:01,700
= Jiaqing Zi =
Act your age! What’s with the rush?

434
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:03,500
Just now, I heard

435
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:05,660
from eunuchs at the Imperial Academy

436
00:30:05,860 --> 00:30:06,820
that after the court adjourned,

437
00:30:06,900 --> 00:30:08,420
officials didn’t leave

438
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:09,340
but were discussing something.

439
00:30:09,700 --> 00:30:10,740
Later,

440
00:30:10,820 --> 00:30:12,660
censors and members of the Remonstrance Bureau

441
00:30:12,780 --> 00:30:14,260
charged into the inner chamber

442
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:15,860
and surrounded His Majesty,

443
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:18,580
forcing him to listen to them.

444
00:30:19,780 --> 00:30:21,060
What are they doing?

445
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:23,540
Are they trying to revolt?

446
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:25,100
No!

447
00:30:25,340 --> 00:30:26,260
They must think

448
00:30:26,260 --> 00:30:27,220
father made a huge mistake

449
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:28,500
by giving Zhang Yaozuo

450
00:30:28,620 --> 00:30:29,780
such high-ranking posts,

451
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:30,860
so they’re determined to change his mind.

452
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:31,820
Stop, Huirou.

453
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:34,020
You know nothing about court affairs.

454
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:36,620
It’s said that Zhang Yaozuo is indeed the cause.

455
00:30:36,660 --> 00:30:37,580
Officials said

456
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:40,020
appointing him Commissioner of Palace Attendants,

457
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:41,100
Chief of the Palace of Sage

458
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:43,140
and Governor

459
00:30:43,540 --> 00:30:44,740
is unprecedented.

460
00:30:45,220 --> 00:30:46,340
What’s more,

461
00:30:46,460 --> 00:30:48,220
that harsh critic Mr. Bao

462
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:49,500
accused His Majesty

463
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:51,020
of misbehaving himself.

464
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:51,780
That’s bad.

465
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:54,300
Commissioner of Palace Attendants takes charge of

466
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:55,460
all inner bureaus, palace attendants,

467
00:30:55,700 --> 00:30:57,180
the promotion and demotion of eunuchs.

468
00:30:57,620 --> 00:30:59,460
If her uncle is in charge,

469
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:00,980
won’t we lose the freedom

470
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:01,980
to choose or keep

471
00:31:02,300 --> 00:31:04,420
our own servants?

472
00:31:06,420 --> 00:31:07,380
Merciful Buddha.

473
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:09,420
I hope those officials can be firm

474
00:31:09,980 --> 00:31:11,420
and change His Majesty’s mind.

475
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:13,700
Another thing is,

476
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:15,700
Noble Consort Zhang and her people

477
00:31:15,700 --> 00:31:16,860
are already outside the Hall of Arch

478
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:17,700
waiting for His Majesty.

479
00:31:18,220 --> 00:31:19,460
She used His Majesty’s kindness

480
00:31:19,460 --> 00:31:20,820
to ask for posts for her family.

481
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:23,500
Has she no shame?

482
00:31:24,380 --> 00:31:26,060
Let’s go to the Hall of Arch

483
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:27,220
to see father.

484
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:28,820
Huirou!

485
00:31:30,020 --> 00:31:31,300
Come back, Huirou!

486
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:34,860
That girl!

487
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:38,300
Over the 30-year reign of His Majesty,

488
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:39,580
he’s adhered to the tradition

489
00:31:39,780 --> 00:31:40,860
without any breach.

490
00:31:41,220 --> 00:31:42,860
Yet over the past five years,

491
00:31:42,900 --> 00:31:44,340
Zhang Yaozuo’s promotion by him

492
00:31:44,380 --> 00:31:46,700
has raised criticisms and warnings from heaven.

493
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,660
It’s not His Majesty’s fault

494
00:31:48,820 --> 00:31:50,140
but caused by the greedy

495
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,500
and shameless member of the harem

496
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:52,700
and her family.

497
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,180
I agree.

498
00:31:54,740 --> 00:31:55,700
Let’s go see Wen Yanbo.

499
00:31:55,900 --> 00:31:57,100
- Let’s go! - Let’s go!

500
00:32:01,980 --> 00:32:04,300
Official posts belong to the public

501
00:32:04,300 --> 00:32:06,100
and should be given to the qualified.

502
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:07,900
How could Your Majesty

503
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:09,620
treat them as gold and silver

504
00:32:09,620 --> 00:32:11,100
and hand them out

505
00:32:11,100 --> 00:32:13,220
to a concubine’s mediocre relative.

506
00:32:13,980 --> 00:32:16,340
Heaven’s sent the warning. People are suffering.

507
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:19,300
Yet that Zhang Yaozuo isn’t affected at all

508
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:21,780
who has shown no regret or remorse.

509
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:24,860
Few are more brazen than him!

510
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,300
I understand your concern, Mr. Bao.

511
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:27,380
I understand.

512
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:37,420
As a court official,

513
00:32:37,860 --> 00:32:39,740
I lost my manners today.

514
00:32:40,540 --> 00:32:42,180
I’m guilty

515
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:44,340
and don’t deserve this hat,

516
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:47,740
but I said all those things

517
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:49,340
for the sake of our state.

518
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:50,540
They’re my heartfelt words.

519
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:54,780
Please dismiss Zhang Yaozuo
from Commissioner of Palace Attendants

520
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:56,500
and Governor.

521
00:32:59,860 --> 00:33:00,780
I have questions

522
00:33:00,780 --> 00:33:02,260
for ministers here.

523
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:07,700
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =

524
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:08,420
What is it?

525
00:33:10,100 --> 00:33:11,620
= Tang Jie, courtesy name Zifang =
Zhang Yaozuo is rising rapidly

526
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:12,540
because of his relationship with Noble Consort.

527
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:14,380
His Majesty couldn’t turn her down

528
00:33:14,980 --> 00:33:16,060
but why didn’t you

529
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:17,500
try to stop His Majesty?

530
00:33:18,220 --> 00:33:19,500
Aren’t you afraid

531
00:33:19,500 --> 00:33:21,820
the disaster in the Tang Dynasty
would repeat itself?

532
00:33:22,580 --> 00:33:24,220
Prime Minister puts the future of the state behind

533
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:26,460
but panders to His Majesty and consort’s family

534
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:28,460
for his own benefit.

535
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:31,060
He should be punished.

536
00:33:31,180 --> 00:33:33,180
Yes. He should be punished.

537
00:33:34,340 --> 00:33:36,460
Governor isn’t a key post

538
00:33:37,100 --> 00:33:38,460
and is only given to Yaozuo for his service

539
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:40,380
and to celebrate Noble Consort’s promotion.

540
00:33:40,980 --> 00:33:42,180
Founding Father and his brother

541
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,900
used to be governors.

542
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:45,620
How is that post not important?

543
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:53,380
I know you’re loyal and honest.

544
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:56,100
You can state your suggestions calmly.

545
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:57,340
This is unnecessary.

546
00:33:57,980 --> 00:33:59,140
As for Yaozuo’s promotion,

547
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:01,060
I’ve explained it repeatedly.

548
00:34:01,500 --> 00:34:03,780
He’s promoted to Commissioner of Palace Attendants

549
00:34:03,820 --> 00:34:06,020
but transferred to Heyang to be the Governor.

550
00:34:06,700 --> 00:34:07,500
As he’s outside the Capital,

551
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:08,820
he can’t interfere in affairs at court

552
00:34:08,820 --> 00:34:09,980
or in the palace.

553
00:34:11,300 --> 00:34:12,860
Zhang Yaozuo abuses Your Majesty’s favor,

554
00:34:12,860 --> 00:34:14,900
disregards the tradition, overreaches himself

555
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:17,020
and asks for promotions more than once.

556
00:34:17,180 --> 00:34:18,980
As Commissioner of Palace Attendants,

557
00:34:19,100 --> 00:34:20,100
although he’s working outside the Capital,

558
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:21,820
he’ll ask to come back to work in the Cabinet

559
00:34:21,820 --> 00:34:23,300
and even become a Prime Minister.

560
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:25,460
Your Majesty, please think twice!

561
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:26,980
Prime Minister Wen Yanbo

562
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:28,020
once offered Noble Consort

563
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:30,140
luxurious silk from Sichuan.

564
00:34:30,180 --> 00:34:32,060
He must be close to Zhang Yaozuo under the table.

565
00:34:32,100 --> 00:34:35,140
Of course he wouldn’t oppose his promotion.

566
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:36,100
Oppose?

567
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:38,180
They’re practically on the same side.

568
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:40,260
Wen Yanbo gained his position in the Cabinet

569
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:41,340
after pacifying Qinghe County.

570
00:34:41,620 --> 00:34:44,220
Didn’t Noble Consort advise him

571
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:46,580
to take that task?

572
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:48,100
Wen Yanbo...

573
00:34:48,580 --> 00:34:51,140
Wen Yanbo abuses his power for personal gain

574
00:34:51,180 --> 00:34:53,100
who’s as evil as Zhang Yaozuo.

575
00:34:53,100 --> 00:34:53,740
Indeed!

576
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:56,540
By supporting Yaozuo,
and allying himself with Noble Consort

577
00:34:56,820 --> 00:34:58,900
he’s destroying His Majesty’s reputation.

578
00:34:59,100 --> 00:35:00,380
Did Noble Consort tip you off?

579
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,140
Did you give gifts to...

580
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:02,660
Did Noble Consort tip you off?

581
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:04,660
- Did Noble Consort tip you off?
- As one of the highest-ranking officials,

582
00:35:04,660 --> 00:35:05,700
Wen Yanbo...

583
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:07,230
- disregards the law and order...
- Did Noble Consort tip you off?

584
00:35:07,286 --> 00:35:07,943
Enough!

585
00:35:08,420 --> 00:35:09,740
Huaiji, go.

586
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:10,620
Ask them to leave.

587
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:12,300
Punish the one framing and scolding Prime Minister

588
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:13,500
for contempt of court.

589
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,420
Drag Tang Jie out.

590
00:35:15,860 --> 00:35:16,460
Yes.

591
00:35:16,460 --> 00:35:17,300
Your Majesty!

592
00:35:18,100 --> 00:35:19,620
When Zhang Yaozuo’s appointment was announced,

593
00:35:19,860 --> 00:35:21,220
the sky suddenly darkened.

594
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:24,180
Shortly after that, an earthquake struck Xiuzhou.

595
00:35:24,300 --> 00:35:25,780
The noise thundered from the northwest.

596
00:35:26,380 --> 00:35:28,460
People should follow heaven’s will.

597
00:35:28,700 --> 00:35:30,700
Your Majesty, please put the state

598
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:31,980
before your love.

599
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:33,900
Dismissing Zhang Yaozuo

600
00:35:33,900 --> 00:35:35,700
from posts he doesn’t deserve

601
00:35:35,740 --> 00:35:37,100
is in the interests of the state

602
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:39,380
and our people, Your Majesty!

603
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:54,660
Father adores you so much.

604
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,860
Why did you put him in this awkward position?

605
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:05,300
What are you doing?

606
00:36:06,540 --> 00:36:07,340
Princess,

607
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:11,700
do you feel good

608
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:13,300
that you’ve got your revenge?

609
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:20,780
All those loyal officials

610
00:36:21,500 --> 00:36:22,700
are condemning your enemy

611
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:25,380
and forcing His Majesty

612
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:28,220
to abandon his love and feelings.

613
00:36:30,020 --> 00:36:31,300
For those around him

614
00:36:32,620 --> 00:36:34,180
who refused to restrain

615
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:35,780
and molded themselves

616
00:36:35,780 --> 00:36:37,140
into Buddhas,

617
00:36:37,860 --> 00:36:40,340
he can’t love them and must give them all up.

618
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:44,940
Is that really good?

619
00:36:46,100 --> 00:36:46,860
Do you think

620
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,140
you’re also a Buddha?

621
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:12,540
= Qinghe County =
♪ Scholars grow ♪

622
00:37:12,780 --> 00:37:22,780
♪ Looking at Liang Garden coming back to class ♪

623
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:32,980
♪ Scholars’ hats and robes
are like stars and clouds ♪

624
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:42,900
♪ Learn classics and read articles ♪

625
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:48,140
♪ Classics are enlightening ♪

626
00:37:48,380 --> 00:37:56,020
♪ Just like the sun lights the world ♪

627
00:37:56,300 --> 00:38:00,620
♪ Articles are educational ♪

628
00:38:00,820 --> 00:38:08,060
♪ Similar to four seasons nourishing the earth ♪

629
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:15,260
♪ Thus such trend is spread nationwide ♪

630
00:38:15,620 --> 00:38:18,980
♪ Scholars grow ♪

631
00:38:19,020 --> 00:38:19,940
Tidy up.

632
00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:21,100
Don’t get wet.

633
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:30,780
♪ Looking at Liang Garden coming back to class ♪

634
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:37,060
= Zhang Maoze, courtesy name Pingfu Bitao =
♪ Scholars’ hats and robes are like stars and clouds ♪

635
00:38:37,060 --> 00:38:40,820
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
♪ Scholars’ hats and robes are like stars and clouds ♪

636
00:38:41,540 --> 00:38:51,060
♪ Learn classics and read articles ♪

637
00:38:51,620 --> 00:38:56,380
♪ Classics are enlightening ♪

638
00:38:56,700 --> 00:39:01,060
♪ Just like the sun lights the world ♪

639
00:39:01,100 --> 00:39:01,980
Mr. Fan.

640
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:06,580
Officer Zhang.

641
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:08,660
♪ Articles are educational ♪

642
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:16,020
♪ Similar to four seasons nourishing the earth ♪

643
00:39:19,660 --> 00:39:21,940
This school provides elementary education.

644
00:39:22,580 --> 00:39:24,980
Farmers’ children come to learn to read

645
00:39:25,180 --> 00:39:26,700
so that they can understand contracts,

646
00:39:27,100 --> 00:39:29,180
and learn to do math and accounts.

647
00:39:30,020 --> 00:39:31,420
We also offer classes

648
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:33,300
to study Essential Techniques for People’s Welfare

649
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,500
and Essential Prescriptions Worth a Thousand Gold,

650
00:39:34,620 --> 00:39:36,100
which are well-received, too.

651
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:39,820
Even some girls

652
00:39:40,340 --> 00:39:42,900
dress up as men to come to study.

653
00:39:47,820 --> 00:39:48,900
Speaking of that,

654
00:39:49,820 --> 00:39:51,020
the Empress did the same thing

655
00:39:51,420 --> 00:39:53,820
to study at Nanjing Academy.

656
00:39:55,300 --> 00:39:58,820
It’s been 20 years.

657
00:40:20,180 --> 00:40:26,860
♪ Thus such trend is spread nationwide ♪

658
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:28,380
His Majesty once said

659
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:30,820
thanks to your guidance,

660
00:40:30,820 --> 00:40:32,300
the Empress is able to be fair and just

661
00:40:32,620 --> 00:40:35,060
and is well-respected for over a decade

662
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:37,740
by court officials and the harem.

663
00:40:40,700 --> 00:40:41,700
Principles should be learned

664
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:44,260
not only to serve the nation

665
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:45,980
but also to be a decent person.

666
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:49,140
The core of your education

667
00:40:49,220 --> 00:40:51,620
is to learn to be a decent man.

668
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:57,780
I was ordered to open free schools in Qinghe County

669
00:40:58,060 --> 00:40:59,580
and told specifically

670
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:02,820
to teach students two works of yours:

671
00:41:03,580 --> 00:41:05,180
Notes on Shangqiu Academy

672
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:06,580
and Notes on Yueyang Pavilion.

673
00:41:11,060 --> 00:41:13,700
His Majesty flattered me.

674
00:41:24,180 --> 00:41:25,540
Following Noble Consort’s promotion,

675
00:41:25,980 --> 00:41:28,260
almost two years of debate

676
00:41:28,620 --> 00:41:30,380
on her uncle’s post

677
00:41:30,620 --> 00:41:32,060
has finally ended.

678
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:35,380
Although he’s Commissioner of Palace Attendants,

679
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:37,020
he only has an honorary title

680
00:41:37,020 --> 00:41:38,260
with little power.

681
00:41:39,340 --> 00:41:40,180
His Majesty also announced

682
00:41:40,820 --> 00:41:42,460
that he’d never be in the Cabinet or Privy Council.

683
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:46,500
Court officials,

684
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:47,860
high or low-ranking,

685
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:51,780
were adamant for the sake of the state.

686
00:41:54,100 --> 00:41:55,460
His Majesty used to joke

687
00:41:55,980 --> 00:41:57,300
that all officials

688
00:41:57,620 --> 00:41:59,420
are like Fan Zhongyan’s disciples

689
00:41:59,620 --> 00:42:00,820
who are candid.

690
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:03,980
I don’t deserve that compliment.

691
00:42:04,620 --> 00:42:06,740
I should write an apology letter.

692
00:42:08,500 --> 00:42:10,300
Make that a thank-you letter.

693
00:42:11,220 --> 00:42:12,300
Last month,

694
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:13,900
His Majesty firmly promoted you

695
00:42:14,380 --> 00:42:15,500
to Vice Minister of Rituals

696
00:42:15,700 --> 00:42:16,940
and appointed Han Qi and Fu Bi

697
00:42:16,940 --> 00:42:18,340
Scholar of Politics.

698
00:42:18,860 --> 00:42:20,060
Many are looking forward

699
00:42:20,620 --> 00:42:22,100
to the return

700
00:42:22,580 --> 00:42:24,300
of reformers like you.

701
00:42:25,980 --> 00:42:29,340
I’m too dull and blunt

702
00:42:29,740 --> 00:42:32,300
to be Prime Minister.

703
00:42:34,620 --> 00:42:36,500
I mean that

704
00:42:36,820 --> 00:42:38,420
with all sincerity.

705
00:42:38,980 --> 00:42:39,820
Mr. Fan...

706
00:42:40,180 --> 00:42:41,540
Over the past years,

707
00:42:42,100 --> 00:42:44,540
I’ve offended His Majesty more than once

708
00:42:44,820 --> 00:42:46,620
and made countless enemies.

709
00:42:47,700 --> 00:42:49,940
And I’ve made

710
00:42:50,180 --> 00:42:51,900
tons of reckless mistakes,

711
00:42:52,220 --> 00:42:53,700
and caused His Majesty trouble.

712
00:42:55,180 --> 00:42:56,980
Now, I’m about to turn 60

713
00:42:57,220 --> 00:42:58,940
and can still be a local governor

714
00:43:00,780 --> 00:43:02,300
and be able

715
00:43:02,340 --> 00:43:04,380
to realize my ambition.

716
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:07,860
Every time I achieve something,

717
00:43:08,380 --> 00:43:11,300
His Majesty will reward me.

718
00:43:13,220 --> 00:43:15,140
You’re loyal, forthright

719
00:43:15,140 --> 00:43:16,380
and selfless.

720
00:43:17,140 --> 00:43:19,620
His Majesty is well aware of that.

721
00:43:21,420 --> 00:43:23,860
Those vicious remarks on the reform

722
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:26,620
did infuriate me at the time.

723
00:43:29,220 --> 00:43:31,540
I had resentment.

724
00:43:32,540 --> 00:43:35,180
Why didn’t His Majesty suppress the opposition

725
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:36,660
to protect the reform?

726
00:43:37,820 --> 00:43:39,660
But after dwelling

727
00:43:39,660 --> 00:43:41,020
on the past decades,

728
00:43:41,580 --> 00:43:43,100
I get it.

729
00:43:45,300 --> 00:43:48,860
= Fan Zhongyan died in Xuzhou in 1052 A.D.
with a posthumous title Wenzheng =

730
00:43:48,860 --> 00:43:52,420
= “Officials at court worry about the masses.
Those outside the court concern about the Emperor”. =

731
00:43:52,420 --> 00:43:56,140
= “Be the first to bear hardships
and the last to enjoy comforts”. =

732
00:43:56,140 --> 00:43:59,700
= Such quotes are still well-known even today. =

